["## Multilayer Chip Ferrite Bead \_ UPZ Series
## FEATURES

- Internal silver printed layers and magnetic shielded structures t0 minimize crosstalk
- Monolithic structure for excellent reliability
- Smaller DC resistance and larger allowable current than PZ series
- Can be used in a wide range of frequency t0 suppress EMI
- Noise suppression for power lines or large current signal lines of electric equipments, such as communication equipments; computers, AV equipments, etc
